{"tid":2105191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃碧雲: 而民調會進行到九月屆時才知會否能參選","createTime":"2020-07-12T12:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T12:52:39.000Z","uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b494a0c37b75c556b65d14255db1dd43bc38ca74","tid":2105191,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075401&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=390818b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075401&h=9f0623f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075401</a><br />\n民調顯示支持率低 黃碧雲：民調有漏洞不能作準<br />\n<br />\n被問到支持率在民調中偏低、會否檢討自己的行事作風時，<span class=\"red\">黃碧雲反指坊間民調有漏洞，「有唔少人開假account，或者開幾個電郵投票」；她批評民意結果有偏差，更指「民調可以一人可投四票，大選就唔會喇。」她又認為，是次初選機制仍未確定最終出戰人數，「而家嗰投票只係排次序」，而民調會進行到九月，故屆時才肯定自己能否參與立法會選舉。</span><br />\n初選未完已經打開口牌話唔會理會初選結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1018a51bd71a76074d84261d48757578da9a4b57","tid":2105191,"uid":224916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"咁咪放長雙眼睇下九月有幾多人投你囉<br />\n<br />\n夠薑開個莊俾我投注，我訓身買你輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}